content.html: BREAKING: In a stunning blow to the Supreme Court's Roe v Wade decision, the federal government says doctors and hospitals MUST provide emergency abortions under federal law when a pregnant woman needs the procedure to be stabilized. Respond YES if you agree this is great news!
